<emphasis id="B95F4E0CB75EFFE0FA69FDB1F899F479" bold="true" box="[1474,1874,522,551]" pageId="25" pageNumber="132">Subspecies and Distribution.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B94921EB75EFFE0FA69FD95F646F411" blockId="25.[1460,2679,282,3466]" box="[1474,2445,558,591]" pageId="25" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="4C2BE99DB75EFFE0FA69FD95F883F411" authority="Linnaeus, 1758" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" box="[1474,1864,558,591]" class="Mammalia" family="Leporidae" genus="Lepus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lagomorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="132" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="capensis">L. ¢c. capensis Linnaeus, 1758</taxonomicName>
— Western Cape Province (South Africa).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B94921EB75EFFE0FA69FDE2F71DF428" blockId="25.[1460,2679,282,3466]" box="[1474,2262,601,630]" pageId="25" pageNumber="132">
