</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B94921EB75EFFE0FA7CFD49F70FF211" blockId="25.[1460,2679,282,3466]" pageId="25" pageNumber="132">
. ¢. atlanticus de Winton, 1898 — Morocco. ¢. carpi Lundholm, 1955 — NW Namibia. granti Thomas &amp; Schwann, 1904 — Northern Cape Province (South Africa). MDD nop hawker: Thomas, 1901 — W Sudan, Eritrea. isabellinus Cretzschmar, 1826 — Egypt, Sudan,Eritrea. Ean mediterraneus Wagner, 1841 — Sardinia. schlumberger: Remy Saint-Loup, 1894 — NE Morocco. sinaiticus Hemprich &amp; Ehrenberg, 1832 — Egypt, Iraq. 
